[
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhang_shi_wu",
    "speaker_name": "张十五",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那时候韩侂胄当权，他力主北伐，与金国开仗。结果打了败仗，金国使者到来，要割两淮之地，还要赔偿军银三百万两。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 4,
    "line_end": 8
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "speaker_name": "郭啸天",
    "listener": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "text": "弟妹，我看还是回避一下的好。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 56,
    "line_end": 58
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "贫道丘处机，路过此地，惊扰了各位。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 98
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_tie_xin",
    "speaker_name": "杨铁心",
    "listener": "char_guo_xiao_tian",
    "text": "大哥，这道长好武艺！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 108,
    "line_end": 110
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_bao_xi_ru",
    "speaker_name": "包惜弱",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这⋯⋯这是什么人？",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 180,
    "line_end": 182
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "speaker_name": "丘处机",
    "listener": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "text": "柯大哥，你我赌一赌，十八年后，让这两个孩子比试一番，瞧是谁强谁弱。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 226,
    "line_end": 228
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": "char_qiu_chu_ji",
    "text": "好！咱们一言为定。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 230,
    "line_end": 232
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_cong",
    "speaker_name": "朱聪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "想不到道长武功盖世，文才也如此隽妙，佩服，佩服。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 228,
    "line_end": 230
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_xiao_ying",
    "speaker_name": "韩小莹",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "咱们七人结义，同闯江湖以来，不知经过了多少艰险。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 236,
    "line_end": 238
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_tie_mu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "铁木真",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好孩子，别怕。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 168,
    "line_end": 170
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhe_bie",
    "speaker_name": "哲别",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "小兄弟，多谢你救了我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 180,
    "line_end": 182
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ma_yu",
    "speaker_name": "马钰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这孩子心地善良，将来必成大器。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 200,
    "line_end": 202
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "兄弟，你我一见如故，请把这件衣服穿了去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 110,
    "line_end": 112
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "大哥，我肚子又饿啦。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 114,
    "line_end": 116
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_han_bao_jv",
    "speaker_name": "韩宝驹",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "靖儿，这是一匹十分宝贵的汗血宝马啊。",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 114,
    "line_end": 116
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "比武招亲，那位英雄上来试试？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 130,
    "line_end": 132
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "杨康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我来试试。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 140,
    "line_end": 142
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_hong_lie",
    "speaker_name": "完颜洪烈",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "众位英雄，请了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 70,
    "line_end": 72
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下白驼山欧阳克，见过各位。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 76,
    "line_end": 78
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "好，好！这一碗'好逑汤'，滋味可真不错。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 98
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "老叫化一生贪吃，为了吃你这小丫头的菜，可把看家本领都教给你啦。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 100,
    "line_end": 102
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "text": "七公，您尝尝我的手艺儿怎样？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 94,
    "line_end": 96
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "娃娃，你媳妇儿煮菜的手艺天下第一，你这一生可享定了福。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 102,
    "line_end": 104
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "你想学什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 106,
    "line_end": 108
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我黄药师行事，向来独来独往，何须向人解释？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 88,
    "line_end": 90
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_cheng_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆乘风",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "师父，弟子不孝，累得您老人家生气。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 90,
    "line_end": 92
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "text": "爹爹，你打死我最好，反正我宁可死了，也决不嫁这坏东西。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 40,
    "line_end": 42
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "text": "药兄，咱哥儿华山一别，多年没会了。承你瞧得起，许了舍侄的婚事，今后你有什么差遣，做兄弟的决不敢说个不字。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 38,
    "line_end": 40
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "嘉宾远来，待我吹奏一曲以娱故人。请坐了慢慢的听罢。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18,
    "line_start": 42,
    "line_end": 44
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "祖师爷，您手创丐帮，传到弟子手里，弟子无德无能，不能光大我帮。今日事急，弟子不得不卸此重担。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 120,
    "line_end": 122
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "孩子，你跪下。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 124
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "text": "师父，您叫我做丐帮的⋯⋯丐帮的⋯⋯",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 124,
    "line_end": 126
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "正是，我是丐帮的第十八代帮主，传到你手里，你是第十九代帮主。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 126,
    "line_end": 128
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老叫化真的不中用了，唉，也不知何时何刻归位，得赶紧把打狗棒法传你才是。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 130,
    "line_end": 132
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_huang_rong",
    "text": "你虽做了帮主，也不必改变本性，你爱顽皮胡闹，仍顽皮胡闹便是，咱们所以要做叫化，就贪图个无拘无束、自由自在。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 132,
    "line_end": 134
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_yang_kang",
    "speaker_name": "杨康",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我是大金国小王爷，岂能与你这草民为伍？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 340,
    "line_end": 342
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_nian_ci",
    "speaker_name": "穆念慈",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你⋯⋯你怎能这样待我？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 25,
    "line_start": 346,
    "line_end": 348
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
    "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "七兄弟死剩一个，留着何用？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 178,
    "line_end": 180
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_yao_shi",
    "speaker_name": "黄药师",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "弹指神通！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 184
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我是周伯通，谁找我打架啊？",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 186,
    "line_end": 188
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
    "speaker_name": "周伯通",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "人这么多啊，热闹得紧，妙极，妙极！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 190,
    "line_end": 192
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
    "speaker_name": "洪七公",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "欧阳兄，老叫化服了你啦，你是武功天下第一！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 230,
    "line_end": 232
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "欧阳锋，我靖哥哥和你击掌相约，饶你三次不死，那知你仍然恃强欺我。你言而无信，尚不及武林中一个无名小卒，怎有脸来争武功天下第一的名号？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 220,
    "line_end": 222
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "有一件事，普天下当真无人及得上你老人家，那就是不要脸天下第一！",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 222,
    "line_end": 224
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谁说你是天下第一？有一个人你就打不过。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 240,
    "line_end": 242
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "text": "此人武功了得，你定然打他不过。他名叫欧阳锋。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 242,
    "line_end": 244
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
    "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我是谁？我在那里？我怎么了？",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 246,
    "line_end": 248
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
    "speaker_name": "郭靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "咱们都打不过你！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 234,
    "line_end": 236
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
    "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
    "listener": "char_guo_jing",
    "text": "靖哥哥，做女婿的该当如此，好得很啊！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 40,
    "line_start": 214,
    "line_end": 216
  }
]
